{"tid":1431326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]引導風向，逆轉大局--應對中共抹黑香港之對策","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:52:44.000Z","uid":282796,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b724ea553663d480afae7ef6e6900b344381c0b","tid":1431326,"uid":282796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"第一次出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家認真睇完先屌都唔遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得依加文宣千祈唔好同中國割裂， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何割裂、反動，革命之類嘅詞都係送把柄俾對面</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相反，我哋要多啲用愛國之類嘅詞戳大陸人嘅G點，用大陸熟悉嘅宣傳語句，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以其人之道還治其人之身</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>例如:</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">//爱国就要帮我们的政府变得更好//<br />\n//港人爱国 良药苦口 忠言逆耳//<br />\n//青年运动 报效社会//<br />\n//富强 民主 文明//<br />\n//香港民主自由是社會主义核心价值观的体现//<br />\n//港人抗争 為我国千万無力上访的同胞发声//<br />\n//香港民主游行成功一步 全中国民主進程迈出一大步//</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做target大陸人嘅文宣唔係妄想爭取佢哋支持或者不反對，而係要令佢哋認清事實</span></strong>。呢啲文宣未必可以即時有效引導輿論，但<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">懷疑不義政權嘅種子一旦種落人心，就會暗地滋長</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸咁多隱憂內患，我哋煲大佢，逼到啲人去到臨界點，就會好似反送中咁爆發。嚴格黎講唔係製造內部分化咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一一我哋係要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「引導中華人民覺醒」；當中共被民意反噬，就會暴露更多致命嘅缺口，令我哋有機會爭取到想要嘅嘢。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>求集思廣益。想知大家點睇，完善策略。</strong>"},{"pid":"852bb616081811ccbe939d7b421f351cd2a27c3b","tid":1431326,"uid":282796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a4a175785328641ca55e295e56f9a510b7a89c","tid":1431326,"uid":282796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c32e6d3e5f877bc6788ceb74850a1531dc0e584","tid":1431326,"uid":282796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca83aeac5e100a1891d1f92be685ed4e2ca17eb","tid":1431326,"uid":120377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"好文共賞，晏d一齊傾！"},{"pid":"ffd6c461863506a59d9ee6b61cb9d4205d60b64a","tid":1431326,"uid":290663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db8a897a6faa929ae95af940535f90d8252801d9","tid":1431326,"uid":263585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。"}]}